## 7. PERMISSIONS & MODULE ACCESS

### RBAC Permission Keys
**Module access:** `MODULE_TABLES_VIEW` | `MODULE_POS_VIEW` | `MODULE_KDS_VIEW` |
`MODULE_DASHBOARD_VIEW` | `MODULE_ADMIN_VIEW` | `MODULE_HR_VIEW` |
`MODULE_INV_VIEW` | `MODULE_PRODUCTS_VIEW` | `SHORTAGES_VIEW`

**POS operations:** `POS_PAY` | `POS_SPLIT` | `POS_PRINT` | `POS_EMAIL_TICKET` |
`POS_EDIT_CUSTOMER_PREPAY` | `POS_EDIT_CUSTOMER_POSTPAY` | `POS_VOID` |
`POS_VOID_ORDER` | `POS_REOPEN` | `POS_VIEW_CASH_REPORT`

**Cash:** `CASH_CLOSE`

### Module Keys (middleware)
`CORE_TABLES` | `CORE_POS` | `CORE_QR` | `CORE_DASHBOARD` |
`MOD_INVENTORY` | `MOD_HR` | `MOD_RESERVATIONS` | `MOD_LOYALTY` |
`MOD_ANALYTICS` | `MOD_QBO` | `MOD_MULTI_LOCATION` | `MOD_API`

