## 8. DESIGN SYSTEM

### Linen System (general app)
- Fonts: Outfit (headings), IBM Plex Sans (body), IBM Plex Mono (numbers/code/amounts)
- `--color-coral: #E8714A` | `--color-sage: #6B8F71` | `--color-accent-blue: #4A90D9`
- `--color-amber: #F5A623` | `--sidebar-bg: #1A1A2E`

### POS Dialogs — Custom Dark Theme (NO shadcn/Tailwind inside these files)
- Files: `client/src/components/pos/PayDialog.tsx`, `SplitDialog.tsx`, `pos-dialogs.css`
- Background: `#0a0c0f` | Surfaces: `#111318` / `#181c22`
- Payment method colors: CASH `#2ecc71` | CARD `#3498db` | SINPE `#f39c12`
- Fonts: Barlow Condensed (titles 800) | Barlow (body 400/500) | JetBrains Mono (numbers)
- **Do NOT refactor these to shadcn/Tailwind — they are intentionally standalone.**

### Category System (2-level)
- TOP categories: prefix `TOP-`, colored segmented controls.
- Subcategories: child of TOP via `parentCategoryCode`, shown as pills.
- Default TOPs: Comidas (emerald) | Bebidas (blue) | Postres (rose) | Alcohol (amber).
- All interactive elements: min-height 48px.

### Google OAuth
- `ux_mode: "redirect"` — NEVER use popups (Safari/iOS blocks them).

---

## 9. PRINT BRIDGE

- Node.js app on Surface Go 3: `C:\Printing\print-bridge\index.js`.
- Connects via WSS: `wss://rms.restlaantigua.com/ws`.
- Auth: HTTP header with `PRINT_BRIDGE_TOKEN`.
- Printer: Hoin H806, `192.168.2.200:9100`, ESC/POS, 80mm.
- **NOT updated by Railway deploys** — updates require manual file replacement on the Surface Go.
- Surface Go has no Git installed.

---

## 10. QBO INTEGRATION

- Async, fire-and-forget — never blocks the cashier flow.
- Idempotent: unique constraint on `paymentId`.
- Retry backoff: 5min → 15min → 1h → 4h → 24h (max 5 attempts).
- Void: payment voided in RMS → void SalesReceipt in QBO.
- Mapping: by category (8 categories → 8 QBO items), not by individual product.
- Callback URL: `https://rms.restlaantigua.com/api/qbo/callback`.
- Tables: `qbo_config`, `qbo_category_mapping`, `qbo_sync_log`.

