## 14. CRITICAL ANTI-PATTERNS — NEVER DO THESE

```
❌  new Date() for business logic          → use timezone.ts utilities
❌  Hardcoded schema name                  → use req.tenantSchema / req.db
❌  DDL without migration file             → always /migrations/*.sql
❌  Email outside email-service.ts         → always use the service
❌  WebSocket auth via query string        → use HTTP headers
❌  Assuming Redis exists                  → guard with process.env.REDIS_URL
❌  react-router                           → use wouter
❌  socket.io                              → use native ws library
❌  Merging QR + Dispatch flows            → they are distinct
❌  Employee deductions visible to staff   → MANAGER only
❌  Recalculating taxes on existing items  → tax snapshots are immutable
❌  getTimezoneOffset() without padStart   → produces non-ISO -6:00 vs -06:00
❌  ON CONFLICT covering only one unique   → must cover ALL unique constraints
❌  Push directly to main                  → always PR through develop first
❌  shadcn/Tailwind inside POS dialogs     → those files use custom CSS only
❌  Assuming code fix cleans old DB data   → write explicit SQL for retroactive fixes
```

